== 2019年 ==
本屆頒獎典禮於美國時間2019年12月12日在美國加利福尼亞州洛杉磯微軟劇院舉行，由加拿大遊戲記者[[傑夫·吉斯利|傑夫·吉斯利]]主持。<ref>{{cite web | url = https://www.gamespot.com/articles/the-game-awards-2019-stream-date-revealed/1100-6469803/ | title = The Game Awards 2019 Stream Date Revealed | first = Jeremy | last = Winslow | date = 2019-09-12 | accessdate = 2019-09-12 | work = [[GameSpot|GameSpot]] | archive-date = 2019-09-13 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190913050917/https://www.gamespot.com/articles/the-game-awards-2019-stream-date-revealed/1100-6469803/ | dead-url = no }}</ref>。各獎項的提名則於2019年11月19日公布。<ref>{{cite web | url = https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/2019-game-awards-full-list-nominees-1255770 | title = The Game Awards Reveals Full List of Nominees | first = Patrick | last = Shanley | date = 2019-11-19 | accessdate = 2019-11-19 | work = [[The_Hollywood_Reporter|The Hollywood Reporter]] | archive-date = 2019-11-19 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20191119233041/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/2019-game-awards-full-list-nominees-1255770 | dead-url = no }}</ref> 頒獎典禮在全球五十多個國家中同步直播。此次也是典禮轉播至印度的第一次。<ref>{{cite web | url = https://venturebeat.com/2019/12/05/the-game-awards-will-its-streamed-broadcast-to-india/ | title = The Game Awards expands its streamed broadcast to India | first = Dean | last = Takahashi | date = 2019-12-05 | accessdate = 2019-12-05 | work = [[Venture_Beat|Venture Beat]] | archive-date = 2019-12-06 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20191206125614/https://venturebeat.com/2019/12/05/the-game-awards-will-its-streamed-broadcast-to-india/ | dead-url = no }}</ref> 

晚會邀請了許多嘉賓。他們包括前任天堂總裁[[雷吉·菲爾斯-埃米|雷吉·菲爾斯-埃米]]，NBA球星[[斯蒂芬·科里|斯蒂芬·科里]]，導演[[強納森·諾蘭|強納森·諾蘭]]，演員[[諾曼·李杜斯|諾曼·李杜斯]]、[[馮·迪索|馮·迪索]]和[[蜜雪兒·羅德里奎茲|蜜雪兒·羅德里奎茲]]，遊戲開發者{{le|中村育美|Ikumi Nakamura}}，[[大青蛙劇場|《大青蛙劇場》]]角色Dr. Bunsen Honeydew和Beaker。<ref>{{cite web | url = https://www.gamespot.com/articles/the-game-awards-2019-presenters-include-reggie-fil/1100-6472044/ | title = The Game Awards 2019 Presenters Include Reggie Fils-Aime And Geoff Keighley's Favorite Muppet | first = James | last = O'Conner | date = 2019-12-09 | accessdate = 2019-12-09 | work = [[GameSpot|GameSpot]] | archive-date = 2020-01-07 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200107014107/https://www.gamespot.com/articles/the-game-awards-2019-presenters-include-reggie-fil/1100-6472044/ | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url = https://www.destructoid.com/ikumi-nakamura-and-reggie-fils-aime-will-guest-present-at-the-game-awards-574799.phtml | title = Ikumi Nakamura and Reggie Fils-Aime will guest present at The Game Awards | first = Chris | last = Moyse | date = 2019-12-11 | accessdate = 2019-12-11 | work = [[Destructoid|Destructoid]] | archive-date = 2020-01-17 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200117192826/https://www.destructoid.com/ikumi-nakamura-and-reggie-fils-aime-will-guest-present-at-the-game-awards-574799.phtml | dead-url = no }}</ref>

在2019年12月12日至14日，與大獎聯動的遊戲節將在[[Steam|Steam平台]]舉辦。屆時，一部分即將發行的遊戲會釋出DEMO版本供玩家在節日期間試玩。<ref>{{cite web | url = https://www.gamespot.com/articles/the-game-awards-will-let-you-try-upcoming-games-on/1100-6472119/ | title = The Game Awards Will Let You Try Upcoming Games On Steam For A Limited Time | first = Jeremy | last = Winslow | date = 2019-12-11 | accessdate = 2019-12-11 | work = [[GameSpot|GameSpot]] | archive-date = 2019-12-11 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20191211215022/https://www.gamespot.com/articles/the-game-awards-will-let-you-try-upcoming-games-on/1100-6472119/ | dead-url = no }}</ref>
